### Signup
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Get all posts (public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts

### Create post (Bearer <token>)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Post 1",
  "content": "Nội dung bài 1",
  "tags": ["spring","angular"]
}

### Update post
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Post 1 (updated)",
  "content": "Nội dung sửa",
  "tags": ["spring","jwt"]
}

### Delete post
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Comments by post
GET http://localhost:8080/api/comments/post/{{postId}}

### Add comment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/comments/post/{{postId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "Bình luận đầu tiên!"
}

### Update comment
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/comments/{{commentId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content": "Sửa bình luận"
}

### Delete comment
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Users (admin tool / demo)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
